description.p:
The following traits have been repeatedly observed and are determined to be the unique characteristics of ‘GG DEL PC06.’ These characteristics in combination distinguish ‘GG DEL PC06’ as a new and distinct Osteospermum cultivar.





1. Large daisy type inflorescence;

2. Pale purple ray florets;

3. Dark blue disc florets; and

4. A free branching habit.
